Setting Sun (Counter)
Level: Swordsage 5
Prerequisite: Two Setting Sun maneuvers
Initiation Action: 1 immediate action
Range: Personal
Target: You

Using your watchful eye and your ability to judge an opponent's actions, you move at precisely the same time your enemy begins to move. 

If an opponent in a square adjacent to you moves, you can initiate this maneuver to move into the space it occupied. This movement does not provoke attacks of opportunity.
